|---------|------------|
| `FIN_PROD_ANALYTICS_TRANSFORM` | Finance, Production, Analytics, Transform workload |
| `MKT_DEV_CAMPAIGNS_INGEST` | Marketing, Development, Campaigns, Ingest workload |
{%- elif object_component_order == "<domain>_<dataproduct>_<env>" %}
| Example | Components |
|---------|------------|
| `FIN_ANALYTICS_PROD_TRANSFORM` | Finance, Analytics, Production, Transform workload |
| `MKT_CAMPAIGNS_DEV_INGEST` | Marketing, Campaigns, Development, Ingest workload |
{%- elif object_component_order == "<env>_<domain>_<dataproduct>" %}
| Example | Components |
|---------|------------|
