## Best Practices

| Guideline | Description |
|-----------|-------------|
| Abbreviate | Use 3-8 character abbreviations for readability |
| Snake Case | Use underscores (`_`) to separate components only |
| Uppercase | All names display in uppercase |
| Self-Descriptive | Names should be intuitive for organizational users |
| No Type Suffix | Don't add `_DB`, `_WH`, or `_RL` |
| 30 Characters Max | Keep names under 30 characters for usability |
| Globally Unique | Names should be unique across all accounts |

